docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md:47:- `onboard_bee.mjs` `DEFAULT_CONFIG`: models without ceiling, advisor with `model`.
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md:48:- `bee_status` + preamble: models line shows only generation/extraction + "ceiling = session model"; advisor line shows `advisor.model`.
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md-49-- Prose: `bee-swarming` SKILL + reference, `routing-and-contracts.md` advisor section, `docs/config-reference.md`, README.
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md-50-- Tests: `test_lib.mjs` model + advisor fixtures rewritten.
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md:51:- Existing repo configs backfilled to the new shape (ceiling removed from `models`, `advisor.model` added).
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md-52-
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md-53-## Consequences
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md-54-
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md:55:- A repo's `.bee/config.json` from 0.1.12/0.1.13 with `models.*.ceiling` still works — the value is ignored, ceiling is the session model regardless.
docs/decisions/0015-ceiling-is-the-session-model.md-56-- Not yet dogfooded end to end; advisor mode in particular still wants a real run.
